@startuml
title Model Lifecycle State Diagram

[*] --> EmptyModel
note right of EmptyModel: Model initialized with no elements\nor relationships
state EmptyModel {
}

EmptyModel --> Populated : Model.add()\nnew elements/relationships
Populated --> ViewReady : Model.add(ArchiType.View)\ncreates nodes/connections
ViewReady --> Serialized : Model.write(writer)
Serialized --> Populated : Model.add_relationship(), Model.add()
Populated --> Invalid : check_invalid_conn()/nodes fail
Invalid --> Populated : fix elements/relationships
Serialized --> [*] : Metadata embedded/expanded

@enduml
